# 0. Simple Web Stack

Domain: foobar.com -> 8.8.8.8
www record -> A record

Components:
- 1 Server
- Web Server (Nginx)
- Application Server
- Application Code
- Database (MySQL)

Explanation:
- Server: machine hosting the site
- Domain: maps name to IP
- DNS: www is an A record
- Web Server: handles HTTP requests
- App Server: runs backend logic
- Database: stores data
- Communication: HTTP/HTTPS over TCP/IP

Issues:
- SPOF
- Downtime during deployment
- No scalability
